title: Pinckneyville Wins West Frankfort Triangular
text:
Pinckneyville Wins West Frankfort Triangular   Oct 1, 2015 at 10:04   Oct 1, 2015 at 11:11 PM CDT 
WEST FRANKFORT -- West Frankfort's girls golf team hosted a triangular with Herrin and Pinckneyville at Franklin County Country Club. 
Pinckneyville won the meet with a 177. West Frankfort finished in second with a 191, and Herrin captured third with a score of 193. 
Herrin's Macey Mooneyham and Pinckneyville's Megan Breslin tied for low medalist with a score of 41.
